<V.Fyodorov@tltsu.ru>.

The files associated with the eskd package (see below for a list)
may be distributed under the terms of the LaTeX Project Public License,
as described in lppl.txt directory macros/latex/base/lppl.txt; either
version 1.1 of the License, or (at your option) any later version.


Files distributed with this package
===================================
eskd.ins            This is the installation script that will produce
                    the class file eskd.cls when run through LaTeX
                    or TeX.
eskd.dtx            documented source file of the eskd package.
example.tex 	    example, needs for making documentation.	
eskd.pdf            pdf-formatted documentation.
example.eps 	    picture for documentation.
eskd.ind	    processed index for documentation.
README              This file.

All files in the eskd package may be distributed under the terms of
the LaTeX Project Public License.


Prerequisites
=============
To use this package, you'll have to have PsCyr installed,
available in ftp://ftp.vsu.ru/pub/tex/font-packs/pscyr/.


Installation
============
 1) Run TeX or LaTeX on eskd.ins.
 2) Put the resulting eskd.cls somewhere where LaTeX will find it.

 For documentation, run LaTeX on eskd.dtx or just read eskd.pdf.
   
